      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/322069.Liane_Moriarty">About Liane Moriarty</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/322069.Liane_Moriarty"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1459827224p3/322069.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/322069.Liane_Moriarty">Liane Moriarty
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
54,184
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer951396470199287902">Liane Moriarty is the author of the #1 <i>New York Times</i> bestsellers <i>Big Little Lies, The Husband’s Secret,</i> and <i>Truly Madly Guilty</i>; the <i>New York Times</i> bestsellers <i>Apples Never Fall, Nine Perfect Strangers, What Alice Forgot,</i> and <i>The Last Anniversary; The Hypnotist’s Love Story;</i> and <i>Three Wishes</i>. She lives in Sydney, Australia, with her husband and two children.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

